name: "Boot Burner" Custom Exhaust for VLX600
description:
Are you tired of your bike sounding like a dry fart in the wind? Bummed that when you roll on that throttle someone asks who brought the power wheels??? 
These Boot Burner Exhaust pipes are Loud and Proud! Built using the TJBC one piece machined DIY exhaust headers, This custom exhaust system bolts on to your bike using 1/2" solid steel collars to replace those wimpy stock aluminum collars. Exhaust comes with new hardware. 

Using these pipes will require a re-jet of your carburetors,however we offer carb kits for both the dual carb and single carb models.

These are a direct bolt on to your bike, simply remove your stock exhaust, sell that fart in the  on fleabay, and bolt these puppies on!

We can leave them raw, or paint them black for you, if you want them chromed or ceramic coated, shoot us an email and we can get pricing for you. 

IMPORTANT! due to the high demand for this exhaust system as used by miscreants everywhere to piss off their neighbors, turn around time is currently 4-6 weeks. sorry for the delay, we are working on a way to remedy this!

name: Velocity Stacks For Dual Carb VLX600 Shadows and 750's
description:
If you remove the airbox on a honda shadow with dual carbs, the carbs will have a hard time creating enough negative vacuum to pull in a steady flow of fuel from the pilot and main jet. the solution to this issue? Velocity Stacks! This allows the carb throat to be lengthened enough so that the engine can maintain vacuum beyond the slide of each carb, as well as allow the air turbulence to be reduced. resulting in a much smoother delivery of air and fuel to your engine. 

Each stack comes with a brass screen to keep out birds, cigarette butts and small children. Each stack attached with 3 small set screws. 

Available in Brass, and Aluminum, polished or raw. 

**At checkout, make sure to send payment as a GIFT, otherwise paypal takes a HUGE cut!**

due to a very high demand for these, please allow several weeks for delivery as these are all custom made per order. Thanks!

name: Single Carb Jet Kit for Honda VLX600
description:
This is a jet kit for the Honda VLX single carb models. If you got a velocity stack from me, you will definitely need to re-jet your carb! 
Anytime a change is made to exhaust or intake, a re-jet is usually necessary. This kit is meant to work with a free flowing velocity stack and a free flowing exhaust system. 

kit includes
48 Slow Jet - x 1
50 Slow Jet - x 1
142 Main Jet - x 1
145 Main Jet - x 1
148 Main Jet - x 1
150 Main Jet - x 1 
2 brass shims to lift your needle. 

if you would like different sizes of slow or main jets, please specify in your notes when you order and I will swap out different main or slow jets.
As an upgrade, if you want to make tuning WAY easier, you can buy the jet kit with a long handle Air/Fuel mixture screw.  When you buy the Mixture screw in the kit, you save $5.00!!!
The screw handle is numbered so you can easily count how many turns in or out you are to make tuning a breeze! 

If you would like to buy the air fuel mixture screw by itself the option is in the drop down menu below. 

please allow 7-10 days for delivery

name: Stainless Bolt Kit For Single and Dual Carb Models Honda Shadow VLX600
description:
The stock bolts on these carbs are phillips head, and after repeated use from jetting or modifications, they can strip out pretty easily. Especially if the bike has been outside, the stock bolts accumulate rust like flies on you-know-what and can become stuck or worse, sheared off. 

This is a stainless steel allen head bolt replacement kit for a single or dual carburetor honda shadow. The single kit includes 4 bolts for the slide cover and 4 bolts for the float bowl. The dual kit has 8 bolts for the slide covers and 8 bolts for the float bowls.

Please allow 7-10 days for delivery
